div>\n\n<p><code><strong>fileName</strong></code> プロパティは、このエラーを起こしたファイルへのパスを含みます。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"description","title":"解説","isH3":false,"content":"<p>この標準外のプロパティは、このエラーを起こしたファイルへのパスが入ります。デバッガーのコンテキストから呼び出された場合、例えば Firefox 開発ツールでは、\"debugger eval code\" が返されます。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"using_filename","title":"fileName の使用","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> e <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Error</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Could not parse input'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">throw</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// e.fileName could look like \"file:///C:/example.html\"</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<p>仕様の一部ではありません。</p>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.Error.fileName","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Error/fileName/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\">\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Error/Stack\"><code>Error.prototype.stack</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Error/columnNumber\"><code>Error.prototype.columnNumber</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Error/fileName\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>Error.prototype.fileName</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"解説","id":"description"},{"text":"例","id":"examples"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"fileName プロパティは、このエラーを起こしたファイルへのパスを含みます。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Error.prototype.fileName","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Error.prototype.fileName","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Error.prototype.fileName","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Error.prototype.fileName","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Error.prototype.fileName","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Error.prototype.fileName","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Error.prototype.fileName","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Error.prototype.fileName","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/error/filename","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/error/filename/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"JavaScript リファレンス"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"標準組み込みオブジェクト"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Error","title":"Error"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Error/fileName","title":"Error.prototype.fileName"}],"pageTitle":"Error.prototype.fileName - JavaScript | MDN","noIndexing":false}}